we are not able to reach asymptotia\nwithin our computational means. This is regrettably the case for\n$\\gamma^\\prime=1$ and $0<\\gamma<2/3$, where we are therefore not able to prove\nor disprove even conjectures about the asymptotic survival probability of the\nparticle.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Nov 2006 10:39:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
